Linux Ubuntu 8.04 Desktop AMD64 Hardy Heron

Released today. This is not a rip. It is the official release spreading.
The tracker is connected to the original Ubuntu release, so you will have thousands of seeders.




Linux has never been better or easier. If you have never tried linux - it is time!


The desktop CD allows you to try Ubuntu without changing your computer at all, and at your option to install it permanently later. This is the AMD64 version, and it will only work on x64 systems.

If you have a slower PC, or Mac try Xubuntu.
If you have a regular machine you might want to begin with Ubuntu i386.

